# TravelPlan: Cape Town solo budget adventure — Munich to Cape Town, 1–21 June 2026

| Day 1 — 2026-06-01 — Departure from Munich | Day 2 — 2026-06-02 — Arrival in Cape Town | Day 3 — 2026-06-03 — Table Mountain intro | Day 4 — 2026-06-04 — First Thursdays culture | Day 5 — 2026-06-05 — Muizenberg surf day | Day 6 — 2026-06-06 — Woodstock market and creativity | Day 7 — 2026-06-07 — Kirstenbosch nature | Day 8 — 2026-06-08 — Cape Point and penguins | Day 9 — 2026-06-09 — Langa community culture | Day 10 — 2026-06-10 — Lion's Head and Sea Point | Day 11 — 2026-06-11 — Robben Island history | Day 12 — 2026-06-12 — Surf progression | Day 13 — 2026-06-13 — Oranjezicht market and Waterfront | Day 14 — 2026-06-14 — Budget wildlife day | Day 15 — 2026-06-15 — Recovery and local museums | Day 16 — 2026-06-16 — Hout Bay and coastal hiking | Day 17 — 2026-06-17 — Bo-Kaap cooking and culture | Day 18 — 2026-06-18 — Table Mountain backup / Signal Hill | Day 19 — 2026-06-19 — Final surf and beach social | Day 20 — 2026-06-20 — Last market day | Day 21 — 2026-06-21 — Departure from Cape Town |
